Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.71,0:00:21.90,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你还是一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.24,0:00:25.27,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我还是一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.39,0:00:31.60,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}倘若能彼此交心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:39.94,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}自那天起 四季更替时光流转
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.08,0:00:45.73,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我只想说 谢谢你伴我至今
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.12,0:00:53.94,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}呵着白气 朝向狭窄的小巷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:00:59.33,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你温暖的手使劲拉着我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.43,0:01:01.29,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}不断前行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.37,0:01:04.49,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}好想马上就亲吻你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.74,0:01:08.19,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}躲在自动售货机背后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.45,0:01:11.64,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}害羞地凝视对方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.88,0:01:17.08,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}温柔的心情洋溢胸口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.34,0:01:20.61,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你还是一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.78,0:01:24.06,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我还是一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.40,0:01:29.50,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}倘若能彼此交心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.62,0:01:31.65,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我们便能融为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.73,0:01:34.85,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}与一份小小幸福的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.12,0:01:38.40,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}似乎就在触手可及的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.60,0:01:41.13,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}能变得如此温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:44.09,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}全因有你
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------EDCN5-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.28,0:22:48.96,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,150)\be1}心儿一紧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.07,0:22:52.53,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,0)\be1}这感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.55,0:22:56.86,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)\be1}是坠入爱河的证据吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.67,0:23:07.67,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}在小小的草坪上 玩耍嬉戏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.76,0:23:13.26,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}那是幼时纯真的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.32,0:23:19.23,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}但我却渐渐感受到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.32,0:23:23.56,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}心底那不断膨胀的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.67,0:23:29.95,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}和你相处那么久
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.08,0:23:34.12,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}都无法向你坦白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.23,0:23:37.53,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}总是绕远路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.00,0:23:43.50,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,150)\be1}在心里紧紧地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.87,0:23:45.93,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,0)\be1}在你身旁静静地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.97,0:23:52.20,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,150)\be1}抱住你 凝视你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.58,0:23:57.46,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}那是小小爱恋的开端
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.59,0:24:01.51,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}虽然此刻还无法开口
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.52,0:24:05.47,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}我喜欢你
