Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.50,0:00:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.45,0:00:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过完年 今天又到新学期
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.81,0:00:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得招新人进茶道部
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.54,0:01:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没进展？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你整个寒假都干啥去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.43,0:01:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年初参拜的时候 感觉不是很不错么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.63,0:01:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.54,0:02:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时还以为会进展神速的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.82,0:02:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 橘纯一比想象中要迟钝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,0:02:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要下狠功夫了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.54,0:02:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.79,0:02:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮你想想可以一口气加速进展的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.10,0:02:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.59,0:02:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实啊 香苗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.74,0:02:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得维持现状也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从幼儿园就一直喜欢纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后一直都是这个感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以觉得没必要突然改变现状
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.84,0:02:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱井…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很高兴香苗这么为我着想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.49,0:02:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.43,0:02:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 道什么歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.99,0:02:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 既然你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.71,0:02:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就默默守护你们两个的发展好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.89,0:03:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 你减得怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在努力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛 正月那时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种诱惑实在太多…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.76,0:03:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.44,0:03:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的情况 不限于正月吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱井 你太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那重了多少
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大满足
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.09,0:03:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.55,0:03:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B套餐真的这么好吃么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥知道我吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到我一个人孤零零在吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错了 没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没看到？那你是怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闻气味就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.95,0:03:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在扯淡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.54,0:04:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是看到盘子了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 要不要去买餐后果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.34,0:04:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可…啊不 还是茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.99,0:04:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来减得怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.52,0:04:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这次应该会顺利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.71,0:04:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.71,0:04:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年初参拜那时不是写在木牌上了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家神社应该还挺灵的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 今天我能不能去茶道部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 欢迎欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐她们也会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.65,0:04:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.49,0:05:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 学姐她们怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.79,0:05:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 说不定是躲起来想吓人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说都不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是美也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.30,0:05:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.55,0:05:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公园
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天去决胜负了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森岛？是森岛学姐么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 森岛遥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的遣犬使
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来吧 小狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～不行～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狗都很听森岛遥的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表演各种技艺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.12,0:05:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们看中了她的统率能力 发起挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,条件是如果我们赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要她加入茶道部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:06:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.76,0:06:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.39,0:06:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天的辉日东 没有蜻蜓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,败因在季节
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是呢 没能招森岛遥入部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 让森岛学姐进来了又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也会跟你们一起毕业啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的也对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.93,0:06:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢 学姐们快要毕业了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 原本还想着要弄部长继任仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.01,0:06:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.60,0:06:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2年生只有小梨穗一个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.44,0:06:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让小梨穗当部长 还需要点勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 我斗胆说一句
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.15,0:06:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单刀直入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢 有没有心正式加入茶道部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 虽然的确是融入这里了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 要么顺水推舟加入 当部长怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？突然就让纯一当部长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.38,0:07:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是名义上的部长 别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有名无实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 难得你们这么看得起我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 现在加入的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还附送她哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 我是赠品么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那双手套 手指部分怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.57,0:07:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始硬套上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手指的血液都快停止流动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过逐渐习惯以后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在完全没这感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 关于茶道部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 会废部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.07,0:08:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我入部时 只有学姐她们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.07,0:08:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够两个人的话 应该还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那学姐毕业以后确实够呛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时部员就剩你一个了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两年来 一直都跟学姐们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉在茶道部已经是理所当然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算知道她们要毕业 也没什么实感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过她们真的要离开呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.19,0:08:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想守护好茶道部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算是回报她们一直以来的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.06,0:08:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:09:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才没听见我肚子在叫么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没听见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认真起来 肚子就饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.26,0:09:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去吃蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我还在减肥…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔吃一下没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.51,0:09:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我请客
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.44,0:09:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.30,0:09:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 只请得起饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我请你吃蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就变成你请客了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用这么急吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的蛋糕说不定会卖光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快 啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.73,0:09:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 多危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用跑吧 梨穗子
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 形状OK
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.67,0:10:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道OK
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.34,0:10:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱情也满分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然纯巧克力是挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.66,0:10:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装点上杏仁或者果仁也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我就装点上这橘皮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.68,0:10:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我全都弄上去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该放不下这么多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞定 弄上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.76,0:10:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好强大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.91,0:10:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.31,0:10:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们是我同班同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.71,0:10:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七咲逢和中多纱江
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打搅了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在做巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你们都有送巧克力的对象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是一起做 然后互送
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.86,0:11:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.33,0:11:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了 多出来的就送你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.65,0:11:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正今年也只能收到我 老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.90,0:11:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有小梨穗的吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//--------------------------以下取自萌月字幕组出品BDRip字幕----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子 是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.83,0:11:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哥哥的女友？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是青梅竹马而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.31,0:11:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前见过面的那位前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 美也
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个巧克力能交给你哥哥一个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我的也
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 但是 的确哥哥现在没有女友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是建议你们别跟我哥来往为好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//--------------------------以上取自萌月字幕组出品BDRip字幕----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 最近梨穗子怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥 小梨穗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯最近啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:12:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么问这问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 之前她还说学姐毕了业会寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.48,0:12:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直说吧 你觉得小梨穗怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她？单纯的青梅竹马啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.28,0:12:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.81,0:12:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梨穗可是很受男生欢迎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班上的男生还说她很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问她有没男朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明我更可爱 我也没男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.89,0:12:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不起人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.54,0:12:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不说这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的很可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确 吃东西时那幸福的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像小动物一样很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 就像腮帮子塞满核桃的松鼠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.55,0:12:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.99,0:13:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你跟小梨穗很般配哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱歌也同意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实很般配
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为啊 之前也说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.94,0:13:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她提起你总是很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天在哪里看到他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他做了什么 之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来梨穗子怎么还没来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 果然是来见她的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.96,0:13:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别误会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是来见我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.94,0:13:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有人气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也…也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想入部了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要在上面签个名就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.58,0:13:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.48,0:13:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别怕 下次再来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.96,0:13:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来有戏呢 各种意义上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:14:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是茶道部 还是小梨穗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡芙？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 会不会很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情人节还是送普通的巧克力比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.30,0:14:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那是巧克力馅泡芙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.67,0:14:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.15,0:14:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过为什么弄成泡芙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.51,0:14:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梨穗 知道泡芙的语源吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古希伯来语中 「泡」是「爱」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「芙」是「咒语」的意思哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.28,0:14:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本就是向心上人求婚时送的点心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前学姐是这么跟我说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好像不太对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 橘应该会很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.93,0:14:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讨厌的一天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有哥们是好同志啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.53,0:14:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘 有客人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱井
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎有好礼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥们 难道你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 羡慕死我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一年里最讨厌这天了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧结束啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别哭别哭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.88,0:15:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棚町 向我伸出爱之手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 送我爱之巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不送人情巧克力的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.66,0:15:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绚辻～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.10,0:15:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我跟棚町一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.36,0:15:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.76,0:15:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年稍微改了一下主意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.37,0:15:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 泡芙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.14,0:15:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来很好吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.73,0:15:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是你亲手做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我赶紧试试
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子也吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:15:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.05,0:16:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是巧克力馅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.12,0:16:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？这就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.55,0:16:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没期待过收谁的巧克力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这冷不丁的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么问这问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.05,0:16:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 只是想这么问罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.36,0:16:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那梨穗子你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.49,0:16:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有喜欢的人么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是很受欢迎么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这么受欢迎啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沾到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.22,0:16:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉子学姐 爱歌学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.25,0:17:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜两位毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.06,0:18:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 小梨穗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.25,0:18:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.09,0:18:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本想赶在学姐毕业前招到新人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来还是没招到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.38,0:18:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.57,0:18:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是应该让真心喜欢茶道的人进来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学…学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梨穗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.08,0:18:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两年能和你一起度过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.50,0:18:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们感到很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.71,0:18:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.88,0:18:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很开心哦 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.17,0:18:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.99,0:18:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟学姐 在一起也
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梨穗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.43,0:19:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后我们也会一直守护着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.80,0:19:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大力支援
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.70,0:19:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.60,0:19:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐们还在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.03,0:19:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.49,0:19:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事找我们么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐 恭喜你们毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.29,0:19:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的祝贺礼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.49,0:19:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我学生生涯的最后一年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.14,0:19:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要贡献给茶道部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.93,0:19:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩梨穗子一个 恐怕茶道部会被废啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐 茶道部和梨穗子就交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你们放心毕业吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.45,0:20:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是梨穗子看中的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.76,0:20:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子气概
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.41,0:20:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.85,0:20:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 没点心哦 梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.27,0:20:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定忘记拿了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看活动室里面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.47,0:20:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 有在好好准备嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:20:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉子学姐 爱歌学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.84,0:21:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.39,0:21:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢两位特意过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 很有架势嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.85,0:21:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.61,0:21:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.51,0:21:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副部长兼新入部员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩果然很般配嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然没看错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.17,0:21:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最佳情侣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.56,0:21:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.20,0:21:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夫妻和和气气兴盛茶道部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.03,0:21:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐 你又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 快准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.24,0:21:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要加油拉新生入部哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,络绎不绝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.84,0:21:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.08,0:21:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 请进
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.18,0:21:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请体验一下茶道部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.31,0:21:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我是个冒失又不可靠的部长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.08,0:21:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但想跟一直在身边支持我的纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.09,0:22:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后也好好运营这茶道部
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.56,0:22:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 希望有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.82,0:22:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将我的心情能传达给他…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.49,0:22:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.83,0:22:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子 吹奏乐部的人什么时候过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.09,0:22:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该很快就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.95,0:22:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经跟他们打过招呼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.37,0:22:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香苗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.31,0:22:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香苗 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.60,0:22:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一 我去看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.44,0:22:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.72,0:22:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别摔跤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.70,0:22:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺带一提 目前仍在减肥
