Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.57,0:24:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 橘 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.61,0:24:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.87,0:24:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 绚辻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.35,0:24:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 好久没做预告了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.92,0:24:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以特来劲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.16,0:24:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.87,0:24:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 下集就到绚辻出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.80,0:24:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.37,0:24:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托手下留情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.01,0:24:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.84,0:24:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包～在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.50,0:24:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集 发现
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.49,0:24:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全靠你了哦 橘
